                     <interp inst="t17860222-32-person472" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I apprehended the prisoner on the cry of the last witness, and brought him back, there was no other person running near there at the time.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860222-32-person473">
